Summary: ParticleProcessMaterial is a resource that holds the configuration for particle systems using GPUParticles2D or GPUParticles3D nodes.

Inherits: Material < Resource < RefCounted < Object

ParticleProcessMaterial holds a particle configuration for GPUParticles2D or GPUParticles3D nodes.
